lead_paragraph: South Korea's Park Sung-hyun charged into an early two-shot clubhouse lead in the second round of the U.S. Women's Open on Friday with the ominous figure of world number one Lydio Ko in hot pursuit.

headline.print_headline: Korean Park Has Clubhouse Lead at U.S. Women's Open
